{"tid":1934553,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"屈臣氏或設本港口罩生產線 李澤鉅：稍後公布消息","createTime":"2020-03-20T04:18:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-20T14:53:45.000Z","uid":41423,"like":138,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"94257323e1014d6c59dcf3a43b01fad1dcac5de2","tid":1934553,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T04:18:54.000Z","msg":"屈臣氏或設立本港口罩生產線!  全城口罩難求，大批市民連日來通宵冒寒排隊搶購，屈臣氏早前曾宣佈，改由在其電子商店售賣口罩，並與社福機構合作，分配部份口罩予有特別需要的長者。而今日長和系今日公布業積，主席李澤鉅在記者答問會時透露，長和旗下的屈臣氏或將在香港設立本地口罩生產線，稍後會有消息公布，暫時不便透露詳情。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1727517/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E5%B1%88%E8%87%A3%E6%B0%8F%E6%88%96%E8%A8%AD%E6%9C%AC%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E7%94%9F%E7%94%A2%E7%B7%9A-%E6%9D%8E%E6%BE%A4%E9%89%85-%E7%A8%8D%E5%BE%8C%E5%85%AC%E5%B8%83%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1727517%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E5%25B1%2588%25E8%2587%25A3%25E6%25B0%258F%25E6%2588%2596%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E6%259C%25AC%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%2594%25A2%25E7%25B7%259A-%25E6%259D%258E%25E6%25BE%25A4%25E9%2589%2585-%25E7%25A8%258D%25E5%25BE%258C%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25B8%2583%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%2581%25AF&d=wsLpXOxElywvcqXyO2fdBL7WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=9c25cce6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1727517%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E5%25B1%2588%25E8%2587%25A3%25E6%25B0%258F%25E6%2588%2596%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E6%259C%25AC%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%2594%25A2%25E7%25B7%259A-%25E6%259D%258E%25E6%25BE%25A4%25E9%2589%2585-%25E7%25A8%258D%25E5%25BE%258C%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25B8%2583%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%2581%25AF&h=d566ba2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1727517/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-